t_23.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmadamebianca.blogspot.com%2F2014%2F04%2Fblog-post_23.html&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzq7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=66dc5601\" target=\"_blank\">http://madamebianca.blogspot.com/2014/04/blog-post_23.html</a><br />\n乜鳩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n何謂Ａ菜<br />\n昨晚看肥媽那平DD節目，她指A菜即油麥菜；其實A菜和油麥菜是兩樣不一樣的東西。或者，不是肥媽「乜都吾識」，是資料搜集的人兄不假求証、網上太多錯料、人云亦云還是以訛傳訛罷。傳媒，尤其是電視節目中「亂放流料」，錯誤不停傳下去；假以時日，錯誤亦變真確了；人類受害不淺。"},{"pid":"4bb239424005be1a57f9ba46db531ff5bdf6e664","tid":1102812,"uid":43350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T01:35:05.000Z","msg":"a菜<br />\n<img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-cFniAnebpEM/U1gmpf6YdPI/AAAAAAAAAZQ/qpoBHaV1qs4/s1600/15+A+chai.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-cFniAnebpEM%2FU1gmpf6YdPI%2FAAAAAAAAAZQ%2FqpoBHaV1qs4%2Fs1600%2F15%2BA%2Bchai.jpg&h=4161bde9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n油麥菜<br />\n<img src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-fD4MgHdWQrQ/U1gl7gV-VnI/AAAAAAAAAYs/92LeTK2IvbI/s1600/16-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-fD4MgHdWQrQ%2FU1gl7gV-VnI%2FAAAAAAAAAYs%2F92LeTK2IvbI%2Fs1600%2F16-1.jpg&h=903ff94c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n味道相似<br />\na菜較甜較幼!<br />\n但絕對係2樣菜黎!"},{"pid":"244a0b18448753e949e375c1ef14f57c1ad4d7e8","tid":1102812,"uid":43350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"120a21898c94b74351ee384e0488956858a1245b","tid":1102812,"uid":217530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:49:06.000Z","msg":"a菜真係好撚好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T01:35:16.000Z","msg":"食開邊到?"},{"pid":"b4bb5acc590e218c89c41fed4825d019eca25909","tid":1102812,"uid":111006,"like":0,"dislike":0